# Mercur API Route Reference

All routes are served from `http://localhost:9000`. The API has **three access contexts**:

| Context | Base Path | Who uses it |
|---|---|---|
| **Admin** | `/admin/...` | Marketplace operators |
| **Vendor** | `/vendor/...` | Sellers / shop owners |
| **Store** | `/store/...` | Buyers / public storefront |

> Authentication uses JWT bearer tokens. Vendor/Admin routes require auth headers.

---

## 🛡️ ADMIN ROUTES

### Sellers (Vendor Management)

| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/admin/sellers` | List all sellers on the marketplace |
| `POST` | `/admin/sellers/:id` | Update a seller (approve, block, edit details) |
| `POST` | `/admin/sellers/invite` | Invite a new vendor to register |
| `GET` | `/admin/sellers/:id/products` | List all products for a specific seller |
| `GET` | `/admin/sellers/:id/orders` | List all orders for a specific seller |
| `GET` | `/admin/sellers/:id/customer-groups` | Get customer groups assigned to a seller |

### Attributes

| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/admin/attributes` | List all product attributes |
| `POST` | `/admin/attributes` | Create a new product attribute |
| `GET` | `/admin/attributes/:id` | Get a single attribute |
| `POST` | `/admin/attributes/:id` | Update an attribute |
| `DELETE` | `/admin/attributes/:id` | Delete an attribute |
| `GET` | `/admin/attributes/:id/values` | List values for an attribute |
| `POST` | `/admin/attributes/:id/values` | Add values to an attribute |
| `GET` | `/admin/attributes/:id/values/:value_id` | Get a single attribute value |
| `POST` | `/admin/attributes/:id/values/:value_id` | Update an attribute value |

### Configuration

| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/admin/configuration` | Get marketplace configuration |
| `POST` | `/admin/configuration` | Create/set marketplace configuration |
| `POST` | `/admin/configuration/:id` | Update a specific configuration entry |

### Orders & Order Sets

| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/admin/orders/:id` | Get a single order (extended with marketplace data) |
| `GET` | `/admin/order-sets` | List all order sets (grouped multi-vendor orders) |
| `GET` | `/admin/order-sets/:id` | Get a specific order set |

### Products

| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/admin/products/:id/applicable-attributes` | Get attributes applicable for a product |
| `GET` | `/admin/custom/product-variants` | List product variants with extended marketplace data |

### Notifications

| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/admin/notifications` | List all admin notifications (order events, seller events) |

### Inventory & Logistics

| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `DELETE` | `/admin/inventory-items/:id/location-levels/:location_id` | Remove a stock location level for an inventory item |
| `GET` | `/admin/stock-locations` | List all stock locations |

### Integrations

| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/admin/talk-js` | Get TalkJS credentials for admin chat |

---

### Commission (admin)

| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/admin/commission/default` | Get the default commission rate |
| `GET` | `/admin/commission/rules` | List all commission rules |
| `POST` | `/admin/commission/rules` | Create a commission rule |
| `GET` | `/admin/commission/rules/:id` | Get a specific commission rule |
| `POST` | `/admin/commission/rules/:id` | Update a commission rule |
| `DELETE` | `/admin/commission/rules/:id` | Delete a commission rule |
| `GET` | `/admin/commission/commission-lines` | List all commission line items |
| `GET` | `/admin/commission/search` | Search commission records |

---

### Reviews (admin)

| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/admin/reviews` | List all product reviews |
| `GET` | `/admin/reviews/:id` | Get a single review |
| `POST` | `/admin/reviews/:id` | Update a review (moderate/approve/reject) |
| `DELETE` | `/admin/reviews/:id` | Delete a review |

---

### Requests (admin — vendor onboarding approvals)

| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/admin/requests` | List all pending/processed vendor requests |
| `GET` | `/admin/requests/:id` | Get a specific request |
| `POST` | `/admin/requests/:id` | Approve or reject a request |

