## 🏪 VENDOR ROUTES

> All vendor routes require vendor JWT authentication.

### Seller Identity

| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `POST` | `/vendor/sellers` | Register a new seller account |
| `GET` | `/vendor/sellers/me` | Get the current seller's profile |
| `POST` | `/vendor/sellers/me` | Update the current seller's profile |
| `GET` | `/vendor/sellers/me/onboarding` | Get onboarding status/steps |
| `POST` | `/vendor/sellers/me/onboarding` | Submit onboarding step data |

### Products

| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/vendor/products` | List the seller's products |
| `POST` | `/vendor/products` | Create a new product |
| `GET` | `/vendor/products/:id` | Get a single product |
| `POST` | `/vendor/products/:id` | Update a product |
| `DELETE` | `/vendor/products/:id` | Delete a product |
| `POST` | `/vendor/products/:id/variants` | Add variant to a product |
| `POST` | `/vendor/products/:id/variants/:variant_id` | Update a product variant |
| `DELETE` | `/vendor/products/:id/variants/:variant_id` | Delete a product variant |
| `POST` | `/vendor/products/:id/options/:option_id` | Update a product option |
| `DELETE` | `/vendor/products/:id/options/:option_id` | Delete a product option |
| `POST` | `/vendor/products/batch` | Batch create/update/delete products |
| `POST` | `/vendor/products/import` | Import products via CSV |

### Orders

| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/vendor/orders` | List orders belonging to this seller |
| `GET` | `/vendor/orders/:id` | Get a single order detail |
| `POST` | `/vendor/orders/:id/cancel` | Cancel an order |
| `POST` | `/vendor/orders/:id/complete` | Mark order as complete |
| `GET` | `/vendor/orders/:id/changes` | Get order change history |
| `POST` | `/vendor/orders/:id/fulfillments` | Create a fulfillment for an order |
| `POST` | `/vendor/orders/:id/fulfillments/:fulfillment_id/shipments` | Mark a fulfillment as shipped |
| `POST` | `/vendor/orders/:id/fulfillments/:fulfillment_id/cancel` | Cancel a fulfillment |
| `POST` | `/vendor/orders/:id/fulfillments/:fulfillment_id/mark-as-delivered` | Mark fulfillment as delivered |

### Returns

| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/vendor/returns` | List all return requests for this seller |
| `GET` | `/vendor/returns/:id` | Get a single return |
| `POST` | `/vendor/returns/:id/receive` | Confirm receipt of returned items |
| `POST` | `/vendor/returns/:id/receive/confirm` | Confirm and finalize return |
| `POST` | `/vendor/returns/:id/receive-items` | Mark specific items as received |
| `POST` | `/vendor/returns/:id/receive-items/:action_id` | Update specific receive-item action |
| `DELETE` | `/vendor/returns/:id/receive-items/:action_id` | Remove a receive-item action |
| `POST` | `/vendor/returns/:id/dismiss-items` | Dismiss return items (not accepted) |
| `POST` | `/vendor/returns/:id/dismiss-items/:action_id` | Update a dismiss action |
| `DELETE` | `/vendor/returns/:id/dismiss-items/:action_id` | Remove a dismiss action |

