## 🛍️ STORE ROUTES (Public / Buyer)

### Sellers / Vendor Discovery

| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/store/seller` | List all active sellers/vendors |
| `GET` | `/store/seller/:handle` | Get a seller's public profile by handle |

### Products

| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `POST` | `/store/products/search` | Search products (powered by Algolia) |

### Cart

| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/store/carts/:id` | Get cart details |
| `POST` | `/store/carts/:id` | Update cart |
| `POST` | `/store/carts/:id/complete` | Complete cart → place order |
| `POST` | `/store/carts/:id/promotions` | Apply a promotion code to cart |
| `POST` | `/store/carts/:id/shipping-methods` | Add a shipping method to cart |
| `DELETE` | `/store/carts/:id/shipping-methods` | Remove a shipping method |
| `DELETE` | `/store/carts/:id/line-items/:line_id` | Remove a line item from the cart |

### Order Sets (Multi-vendor Orders)

| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/store/order-set` | List the customer's order sets |
| `GET` | `/store/order-set/:id` | Get a specific order set (contains sub-orders per vendor) |

### Shipping Options

| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/store/shipping-options` | List available shipping options for a cart |
| `GET` | `/store/shipping-options/return` | List available return shipping options |

### Returns

| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `POST` | `/store/returns` | Initiate a return |
| `GET` | `/store/returns/:id` | Get a return status |

### Wishlists

| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/store/wishlist` | Get the current customer's wishlist |
| `POST` | `/store/wishlist` | Create a wishlist or add a product |
| `DELETE` | `/store/wishlist/product/:reference_id` | Remove a product from wishlist |

---

### Reviews (store)

| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/store/reviews` | List reviews (filter by product_id) |
| `POST` | `/store/reviews` | Create a new review |
| `GET` | `/store/reviews/:id` | Get a specific review |
| `POST` | `/store/reviews/:id` | Update a review (within edit window) |
| `DELETE` | `/store/reviews/:id` | Delete a review |

---

### Requests (store — return requests)

| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `POST` | `/store/return-request` | Submit a return request |
| `GET` | `/store/return-request/:id` | Get status of a return request |

---

## 🪝 Webhooks

| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `POST` | `/hooks/payouts` | Stripe webhook endpoint for payout events (split payment confirmations, reversals) |

---

## Summary Count

| Context | Route Count |
|---|---|
| Admin | ~40 routes |
| Vendor | ~120 routes |
| Store | ~20 routes |
| Webhooks | 1 |
| **Total** | **~181 routes** |
